Package: CoMMA
Title: Comparison of Microbial Methylated Adenines
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Carl", "Stone", , "carl.j.stone@vanderbilt.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0232-5223"))
Description: Comparative adenine methylomics between bacterial samples. This package can take methylated adenine calls from nanopore sequencing as input, then characterize methylation throughout the genome, identify differentially methylated sites between samples, and compare full adenine methylomes between samples.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
